<!DOCTYPE html>
<!-- Contact display id and about display id -->
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Main</title>
        <link href="main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <img id="background" src="./img/background.jpg">
        <div id='top_menu'>
            <div id="logo"></div>
            <button id="main" class="top_but">MAIN</button>
            <button id="contact" class="top_but">Contact</button>
            <button id="about" class="top_but">About Us</button>
        </div>
        <div id="main_display" class="displays">
            <div id="no_address" style="display: none;">
                <p1>Please enter your address to continue as a guest</p1>
                <div id="address_div">
                    <input type="text" id='address_input'>
                    <button type="submit" id="address_submit">Submit</button>
                </div>
                <p2>If you have an account, press login!</p2>
                <div id="login_div">
                    <button type="submit" id="login_submit">Sign In</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="yes_address" style="display: none;">
                <div id="user_info">
                    <div id="username_info">
                        username: <br><br>{{{username}}}
                    </div>
                    <div id="address_info">
                        address: <br><br>{{{address}}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id='re_address'>Re-type<br>address</button>
            </div>
            <script>
                if ({{{validity}}} == 0){
                    document.getElementById("no_address").style.display = "block";
                    document.getElementById("yes_address").style.display = "none";
                }else if({{{validity}}} == 1){
                    document.getElementById("no_address").style.display = "none";
                    document.getElementById("yes_address").style.display = "block";
                }
            </script>
            <div id="instruction">
                <p3>어서와 처음이지? Here is the basic step you can follow!</p3>
                <p4>This is instructions</p4>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" id="next_submit">Next</button>
        </div>
        <div id="contact_display" class="displays" style="display:none;">
            <p5>CONTACT INFORMATION</p5>
            <div id="separator" class="top_sep"></div>
            <div id="map"></div>
            <div id="info">
                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <br>
                Here at k2 we always look forward to hearing from you. What is your favourite food? Do you prefer Ramen noodles or Thai food ? Where is your favourite Italian restaurant? Do you like your steak rare, medium or well-done? Tell us what you like!
                <br><br><a href="mailto:yeonjae.jay.kim@gmail.com">yeonjae.jay.kim@gmail.com</a>
                <div id="separator" class="con_sep"></div>
                <br><br><br><h2>RESTAURANT</h2>
                <div id="separator" class="res_sep"></div>
                <p>
                    Would you like to become a k2 partner restaurant? Or are you already a partner of ours and have questions about the service? Then get in touch with us at:
                <br><br>
                <a href="mailto:yeonjae.jay.kim@gmail.com">yeonjae.jay.kim@gmail.com</a>
                <br>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="about_display" class="displays" style="display:none;">
            <div id="about_header">
                <h1>Visual ordering makes the devision-making process delightful and quick.</h1>
            </div>
            <div id="about_info">
                <div id="about_left">
                    <h4>Our Mission</h4>
                    <h2>To provide the best digital food ordering experience</h2>
                </div>
                <div id="about_right">
                    <p>
                        Lazymeal is an online food marketplace featuring high quality photos founded in Vancouver BC, serving consumers, offices and local restaurants.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Lazymeal‘s goal is to offer an online food ordering experience that is second to none. Eating is a daily event for everyone. We believe it should be something enjoyable and fulfilling. Lazymeal strives to be a convenient, easy, and reliable option for everyone who needs to order food on-demand or in advance.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <img id="about_img" src="./img/about.jpg">
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="main.js"></script>
        <script async defer
        src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyCOYA62OBwbkCp7SgiDlDYLCdJOIv1fySY&callback=initMap">
        </script>
    </body>
</html>